nsq + docker
============


This document details how to configure a docker+nsq environment.  Nsqd and nsqlookup will be in separate containers. 

# Links

* [nsq](http://nsq.io/)
* nsqd [container](https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/rexposadas/nsqd/).  There is an [official container](https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/mreiferson/nsqd/) but that does not allow us to connect to an nsqlookupd instance running inside a docker container.
* nsqlookupd [official container](https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/mreiferson/nsqlookupd/)

